1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 33=

3
00:00:26,079 --> 00:00:27,359
I'm not trying to flatter you,

4
00:00:27,960 --> 00:00:30,079
but your trick of
pretending to be candidates

5
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:31,359
is truly brilliant.

6
00:00:31,359 --> 00:00:32,000
Look,

7
00:00:32,159 --> 00:00:33,920
who would suspect us on the street?

8
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:34,960
We're walking openly.

9
00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:36,719
Since it's an examination year,

10
00:00:37,600 --> 00:00:38,719
there are so many candidates

11
00:00:38,799 --> 00:00:40,799
that the officers
are too lazy to check them.

12
00:00:47,719 --> 00:00:48,280
Yunchang,

13
00:00:48,679 --> 00:00:49,280
quick!

14
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:00,500
Don't light the candle.

15
00:01:00,700 --> 00:01:01,990
Otherwise, we'll be discovered.

16
00:01:02,719 --> 00:01:03,840
It's fine, Yunchang.

17
00:01:04,159 --> 00:01:05,599
I've coated these windows

18
00:01:05,599 --> 00:01:08,280
with a special potion Master developed.

19
00:01:08,719 --> 00:01:09,840
From the outside,

20
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:11,400
not a single ray of light can be seen.

21
00:01:11,719 --> 00:01:14,280
We can light as many candles
as we want in here.

22
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:18,079
Dongfang Bai is really amazing.

23
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:27,879
These flowers are all ruined.

24
00:01:30,159 --> 00:01:32,120
Flowers can be replanted.

25
00:01:33,030 --> 00:01:34,500
It's fine as long as people are safe.

26
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:38,879
Alright,

27
00:01:38,879 --> 00:01:40,239
I'll go cook something for you.

28
00:01:40,239 --> 00:01:41,200
You wait here.

29
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:52,120
Flowers can be replanted,

30
00:01:55,239 --> 00:01:56,319
but what about people?

31
00:02:04,100 --> 00:02:06,437
(Ministry of Justice)

32
00:02:07,687 --> 00:02:09,125
(Auspiciousness)

33
00:02:25,759 --> 00:02:27,360
Wuxia, if you're bored, just go outside.

34
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,400
Your presence is annoying.

35
00:02:29,319 --> 00:02:29,919
I...

36
00:02:31,039 --> 00:02:32,879
I'm just happy for Master.

37
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:35,120
Yu, you...

38
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,400
Is it time?

39
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,880
Have you really made up your mind?

40
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:48,759
If you regret it, speak up now.

41
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:50,690
Once you perform the ceremony,
it'll be too late.

42
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,159
It smells so good.

43
00:03:20,510 --> 00:03:21,800
The auspicious hour has arrived.

44
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:24,919
(Incorruptible and Upright, Happiness)
The groom and bride may enter.

45
00:03:25,010 --> 00:03:26,510
- Congratulations!
- Congratulations!

46
00:03:26,610 --> 00:03:27,960
- Congratulations!
- Congratulations!

47
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:29,080
Congratulations!

48
00:03:29,639 --> 00:03:31,199
(Auspiciousness)
Congratulations, congratulations!

49
00:03:32,275 --> 00:03:33,675
(Incorruptible and Upright, Happiness)

50
00:03:33,719 --> 00:03:34,759
So beautiful!

51
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,479
What a perfect match!

52
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:43,759
- Good!
- Good!

53
00:03:43,759 --> 00:03:44,520
Congratulations!

54
00:03:44,879 --> 00:03:45,639
Congratulations!

55
00:03:45,700 --> 00:03:46,312
(Incorruptible and Upright, Happiness)

56
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,000
Good!

57
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:47,879
Congratulations, Chief Mao.

58
00:03:47,879 --> 00:03:49,520
First bow to Heaven and Earth.

59
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:52,960
- Good!
- Good!

60
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:57,990
They're bowing to Heaven and Earth.

61
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,520
- Good!
- Good!

62
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,719
Second bow to the parents.

63
00:04:07,159 --> 00:04:08,759
- Keep going!
- Bow to the parents.

64
00:04:11,319 --> 00:04:12,240
Bowing to the parents.

65
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:18,639
Good.

66
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:19,439
Buyu, come.

67
00:04:19,439 --> 00:04:20,480
Rise quickly.

68
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,600
Buyu, Wushuang,

69
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:22,480
rise quickly.

70
00:04:22,639 --> 00:04:24,519
Husband and wife, bow to each other.

71
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:25,839
Good!

72
00:04:26,879 --> 00:04:28,079
May you have a son soon.

73
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:29,199
Indeed.

74
00:04:30,879 --> 00:04:32,000
A long and happy marriage.

75
00:04:32,079 --> 00:04:33,879
- Congratulations!
- Congratulations!

76
00:04:33,879 --> 00:04:35,120
- Good!
- Good!

77
00:04:48,199 --> 00:04:49,160
Bow.

78
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:51,959
Yu.

79
00:04:53,839 --> 00:04:54,480
Buyu.

80
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,680
Buyu.

81
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:05,040
Husband and wife, bow to each other.

82
00:05:07,439 --> 00:05:09,040
This is delaying the auspicious hour.

83
00:05:12,839 --> 00:05:14,639
The bride is right here.

84
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,120
Who is that?

85
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:19,040
- Look over there.
- Who is that?

86
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:19,879
Who is she?

87
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,319
Mao Buyu,

88
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:48,319
do you remember what you once told me?

89
00:05:50,879 --> 00:05:51,480
Chang,

90
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:53,680
you're the one I chose at first sight.

91
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:55,330
I'm determined to marry only you.

92
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,439
You won't regret it?

93
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:59,160
No matter what happens in the future,

94
00:05:59,399 --> 00:06:00,560
you'll never give up on me?

95
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:01,399
Of course.

96
00:06:27,439 --> 00:06:28,040
Shuang!

97
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:30,399
Release arrows!

98
00:06:32,439 --> 00:06:33,040
Stop!

99
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:41,639
Mao Buyu!

100
00:06:41,639 --> 00:06:42,240
Shuang.

101
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,160
Let's go.

102
00:06:55,050 --> 00:06:55,839
- Don't go!
- Buyu!

103
00:06:55,839 --> 00:06:56,439
Buyu!

104
00:07:03,937 --> 00:07:08,000
♪Memories are scattered by the wind♪

105
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,000
Commissioner,

106
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:09,920
please show some mercy.

107
00:07:09,950 --> 00:07:12,662
♪The clouds remember that clarity♪

108
00:07:13,037 --> 00:07:15,775
♪If the vow was a mistake♪

109
00:07:15,839 --> 00:07:16,560
Move aside!

110
00:07:17,519 --> 00:07:19,120
Grandfather, weapons know no distinction.

111
00:07:19,130 --> 00:07:20,519
There are so many
distinguished guests here.

112
00:07:20,519 --> 00:07:21,920
You must not, Grandfather.

113
00:07:22,012 --> 00:07:25,400
♪Even if time stands still♪

114
00:07:25,487 --> 00:07:30,812
♪I will cross
the sea of stars and clouds♪

115
00:07:30,925 --> 00:07:33,150
♪Only my longing♪

116
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:37,040
This is a special medicine
my master developed.

117
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:39,040
Pretty insane, isn't it?

118
00:07:39,900 --> 00:07:40,680
Quick, after them!

119
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:44,100
♪Deep in my heart, I still cherish♪

120
00:07:44,212 --> 00:07:47,775
♪The phrase which has never faded♪

121
00:07:48,662 --> 00:07:50,925
♪The moment I turned around♪

122
00:07:51,025 --> 00:07:53,362
♪A tear fell from my eyes♪

123
00:07:53,362 --> 00:07:57,562
♪Granting me an eternal galaxy♪

124
00:07:57,675 --> 00:08:01,838
♪I keep our past life's promise
in my dreams♪

125
00:08:01,900 --> 00:08:06,000
♪Stepping through the cracks of time♪

126
00:08:08,839 --> 00:08:09,519
Wushuang,

127
00:08:10,959 --> 00:08:12,399
Mao Buyu's heart belongs to another.

128
00:08:13,500 --> 00:08:15,399
He isn't someone
you can entrust your life to.

129
00:08:15,450 --> 00:08:19,712
♪My dream is you♪

130
00:08:20,199 --> 00:08:22,480
You knew
about this all along, didn't you?

131
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:24,680
I...

132
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:27,720
Did you tell Chu Yunchang
to crash the wedding?

133
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,199
No.

134
00:08:29,400 --> 00:08:33,387
♪Never to part in this life♪

135
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:35,600
I'm going to tear Chu Yunchang
into a thousand pieces.

136
00:08:36,559 --> 00:08:39,240
I'm going to tear Chu Yunchang
into a thousand pieces!

137
00:08:44,137 --> 00:08:47,897
I'm going to tear Chu Yunchang
into a thousand pieces!

138
00:08:56,337 --> 00:09:00,850
♪When the dream ends♪

139
00:09:01,250 --> 00:09:04,637
♪I meet you♪

140
00:09:05,425 --> 00:09:06,975
(Meditation Hall)

141
00:09:23,679 --> 00:09:24,600
It really is you.

142
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,360
Let me look at you.

143
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,600
I missed you so much.

144
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:34,971
I wasn't the one who shot that arrow.

145
00:09:38,799 --> 00:09:40,879
And I didn't really want
to marry Shen Liefeng.

146
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:51,500
Do you have any idea
how dangerous it is here?

147
00:09:53,039 --> 00:09:54,840
Was I supposed
to just stand by and watch

148
00:09:54,850 --> 00:09:55,960
as you married Luo Wushuang?

149
00:09:56,380 --> 00:09:58,279
You should know
that you're the only one I love.

150
00:09:58,519 --> 00:10:00,639
Didn't we agree to split up back then?

151
00:10:00,650 --> 00:10:02,840
I was investigating at the Gate Bureau,
and you went to Chengdu.

152
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:04,090
Why did you come here all of a sudden?

153
00:10:05,875 --> 00:10:10,960
(Sacrifice for Justice)

154
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,000
Deploy the tracking dogs.

155
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:14,480
I had already sprinkled
a special scented powder

156
00:10:14,639 --> 00:10:16,320
onto Mao Buyu's wedding robes.

157
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:19,039
The tracking dogs will find

158
00:10:19,039 --> 00:10:21,080
Mao Buyu's hiding place in no time.

159
00:10:21,399 --> 00:10:22,000
Yes, sir.

160
00:10:27,559 --> 00:10:30,320
When we went
our separate ways a while ago,

161
00:10:31,279 --> 00:10:33,480
you had Wuxia stay
by my side to protect me

162
00:10:33,650 --> 00:10:35,279
because you were afraid
I'd be in danger.

163
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:38,519
I worry about your safety just the same.

164
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,639
I know you only pretended to marry

165
00:10:40,639 --> 00:10:42,000
Luo Wushuang to solve the case.

166
00:10:43,039 --> 00:10:43,759
But

167
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:47,200
you must have reached a dead end.

168
00:10:47,759 --> 00:10:49,240
That's why I had to come help you.

169
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:50,720
Chang,

170
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:53,580
the Luo family
won't let you get away with this.

171
00:10:53,700 --> 00:10:55,440
Once you fall into
the hands of the Gate Bureau,

172
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,810
you'll surely face the death penalty.

173
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:57,879
I leave

174
00:10:58,759 --> 00:11:00,320
and leave you to face this all alone?

175
00:11:01,279 --> 00:11:02,080
Trust me.

176
00:11:02,679 --> 00:11:03,559
I have a plan.

177
00:11:07,039 --> 00:11:08,550
- I have something...
- I have something to give you.

178
00:11:45,399 --> 00:11:46,320
They've caught up to us.

179
00:11:46,759 --> 00:11:49,480
It seems Luo Shixun and the rest
had a backup plan all along.

180
00:11:50,279 --> 00:11:51,639
Chang, listen to me.

181
00:11:51,639 --> 00:11:52,480
Escape through the back door.

182
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,399
I'll cover you.

183
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:54,600
I'm not leaving.

184
00:11:54,700 --> 00:11:56,080
I can't let you
get dragged down with me.

185
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:56,679
Don't worry.

186
00:11:56,679 --> 00:11:57,559
I'm an Embroidered Guard.

187
00:11:57,559 --> 00:11:58,679
They won't do anything to me.

188
00:11:58,919 --> 00:11:59,720
Well, we can't

189
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:01,039
both die here, right?

190
00:12:02,919 --> 00:12:03,799
How about this, Buyu?

191
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,350
You take me out as your prisoner.

192
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:06,840
The credit for capturing
the Jade Squirrel

193
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:09,519
and the leader of the Sacred Hand Sect
will all go to you.

194
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,679
What are you talking about?

195
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:12,519
Hurry up,

196
00:12:12,519 --> 00:12:13,720
or it'll be too late.

197
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:15,279
No.

198
00:12:15,279 --> 00:12:16,679
Stab me with your sword right now,

199
00:12:16,679 --> 00:12:17,559
then make your escape.

200
00:12:17,559 --> 00:12:18,990
They won't make things difficult for me.

201
00:12:20,919 --> 00:12:21,600
Chang...

202
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:25,840
Commissioner,

203
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,039
should we move in?

204
00:12:27,639 --> 00:12:29,879
No rush. Let's watch the show.

205
00:12:36,120 --> 00:12:36,879
Mao Buyu,

206
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:38,759
you heartless man!

207
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:39,840
Shut up.

208
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,120
Buyu.

209
00:12:47,879 --> 00:12:50,279
My grandson-in-law, did you capture her?

210
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:52,000
I intended to beat them
at their own game

211
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:53,159
and catch them all in one go.

212
00:12:53,879 --> 00:12:55,639
But who knew
she was the only one inside?

213
00:12:56,220 --> 00:12:58,240
I had no choice
but to capture Chu Yunchang first.

214
00:12:58,639 --> 00:13:00,080
Beating them at their own game,

215
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:02,120
you are brave and wise.

216
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:05,159
Come,

217
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:07,159
take her to death row.

218
00:13:07,919 --> 00:13:08,559
Wait.

219
00:13:11,759 --> 00:13:12,440
Chu Yunchang,

220
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:14,879
there is no escape for you now.

221
00:13:15,559 --> 00:13:16,480
For old time's sake,

222
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:18,799
walk the rest of this path yourself.

223
00:13:32,137 --> 00:13:35,350
(Ministry of Justice)

224
00:13:47,799 --> 00:13:49,240
I'm leaving now, Master.

225
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:55,879
Wushuang.

226
00:13:58,440 --> 00:13:59,320
I heard

227
00:14:00,350 --> 00:14:02,360
that you were the one
who captured Chu Yunchang.

228
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:10,039
Yu,

229
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:12,039
our wedding was interrupted.

230
00:14:12,039 --> 00:14:12,840
We'll pick another auspicious day.

231
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:13,399
Wushuang.

232
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:17,360
This wedding shouldn't
have happened between us.

233
00:14:18,570 --> 00:14:20,950
Even though the Jade Squirrel
has been brought to justice,

234
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:22,360
after all these years,

235
00:14:22,820 --> 00:14:24,360
I still need some time to clear my head.

236
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:26,120
You should think things over too.

237
00:14:26,879 --> 00:14:27,799
I'll take my leave.

238
00:14:40,799 --> 00:14:41,440
Yu,

239
00:14:42,799 --> 00:14:44,879
why must you fail me?

240
00:14:53,519 --> 00:14:55,000
I treat you so well.

241
00:14:56,120 --> 00:14:57,240
I love you so much.

242
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:59,360
You still can't forget
Chu Yunchang, right?

243
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:03,320
Chu Yunchang...

244
00:15:04,759 --> 00:15:06,120
Once I kill Chu Yunchang,

245
00:15:06,679 --> 00:15:07,879
Yu will be mine.

246
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:10,600
Chu Yunchang, this is all your fault.

247
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:15,759
Yunchang, don't worry.

248
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:17,360
Even if Master ignores you,

249
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:19,120
I will never stand by and do nothing.

250
00:15:24,879 --> 00:15:25,600
Wushuang?

251
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:28,120
What are you doing?

252
00:15:30,799 --> 00:15:31,840
Take her out for me.

253
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:32,600
Yes, ma'am.

254
00:15:32,799 --> 00:15:33,679
I can walk myself.

255
00:15:58,559 --> 00:15:59,279
Luo Wushuang!

256
00:16:02,480 --> 00:16:03,159
What do you want?

257
00:16:03,639 --> 00:16:04,960
I'll tell Grandfather.

258
00:16:05,519 --> 00:16:06,919
Grandfather won't let me kill her.

259
00:16:07,039 --> 00:16:09,200
He said she must be kept
for public execution.

260
00:16:10,639 --> 00:16:12,720
But Grandfather didn't say
I couldn't torture her.

261
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:15,759
As long as I keep her breathing,

262
00:16:16,919 --> 00:16:18,600
Grandfather won't punish me.

263
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:21,279
You really love abusing your power, huh?

264
00:16:21,639 --> 00:16:22,879
You're the one who forced me.

265
00:16:23,159 --> 00:16:24,840
You're nothing but a wicked thief.

266
00:16:24,840 --> 00:16:26,720
You don't deserve Buyu's love at all.

267
00:16:27,525 --> 00:16:29,165
Wicked?

268
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:31,679
Compared to the Luo family,

269
00:16:32,399 --> 00:16:33,559
I still have a long way to go.

270
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,840
Stubborn even when facing death, huh?

271
00:16:37,240 --> 00:16:38,080
Luo Wushuang,

272
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,279
if you actually do this,

273
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:42,320
Mao Buyu will only loathe you more.

274
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:43,039
Shut up!

275
00:16:43,879 --> 00:16:45,639
You're not worthy
of mentioning his name.

276
00:16:46,100 --> 00:16:48,000
Buyu comes from a family
of legendary constables.

277
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:49,559
He detests evil
and knows right from wrong.

278
00:16:49,559 --> 00:16:50,600
It's all because of you!

279
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:53,000
It's you who bewitched him
and turned him into this man

280
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,399
who can't tell right from wrong!

281
00:16:55,240 --> 00:16:56,519
He has his own judgment.

282
00:16:56,519 --> 00:16:57,990
He doesn't need anyone to bewitch him.

283
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:01,960
Don't you just rely on

284
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:03,840
that pretty face of yours?

285
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:06,559
I'll ruin it today.

286
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:09,039
I want to see if Buyu

287
00:17:10,279 --> 00:17:11,680
will still love you then.

288
00:17:12,079 --> 00:17:12,799
You wouldn't dare.

289
00:17:13,079 --> 00:17:14,160
What wouldn't I dare?

290
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:16,039
This is the Gate Bureau,
my family's territory.

291
00:17:16,519 --> 00:17:17,359
Hold her down!

292
00:17:18,440 --> 00:17:19,160
Luo Wushuang,

293
00:17:19,279 --> 00:17:20,000
enough is enough.

294
00:17:20,079 --> 00:17:21,150
How long will you stay mad?

295
00:17:21,240 --> 00:17:22,440
Aren't you afraid of karma?

296
00:17:22,799 --> 00:17:24,279
You forced my hand, Chu Yunchang!

297
00:17:24,279 --> 00:17:25,400
You forced me.

298
00:17:25,599 --> 00:17:26,440
Go die!

299
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:42,675
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

300
00:17:42,713 --> 00:17:45,588
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

301
00:17:46,088 --> 00:17:51,806
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

302
00:17:52,988 --> 00:17:56,308
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

303
00:17:56,438 --> 00:17:59,358
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

304
00:18:00,526 --> 00:18:05,766
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

305
00:18:06,988 --> 00:18:09,381
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

306
00:18:09,381 --> 00:18:13,031
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

307
00:18:13,112 --> 00:18:16,602
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

308
00:18:16,688 --> 00:18:19,663
♪To the ends of time♪

309
00:18:19,663 --> 00:18:23,038
♪The moon traces your face♪

310
00:18:23,225 --> 00:18:26,813
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

311
00:18:26,813 --> 00:18:33,053
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

312
00:18:33,388 --> 00:18:36,603
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

313
00:18:36,888 --> 00:18:40,426
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

314
00:18:40,713 --> 00:18:43,738
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

315
00:18:43,738 --> 00:18:46,838
♪On our way to forever♪

316
00:18:46,838 --> 00:18:50,688
♪The moon traces your face♪

317
00:18:50,688 --> 00:18:54,048
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

318
00:18:54,238 --> 00:19:00,198
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

319
00:19:01,275 --> 00:19:10,915
♪Just to be with you♪
